item.title: Chitra Pournami Vilakku Puja
item.description: Register for Online Vilakku Puja. Cost will be $9 for each participating person. Please add each participant detail and then add them to the cart. After all participants are added, then proceed to "Checkout via PayPal" link below. If you are signing up for multiple members in your household, enter the same email-address. If you are sponsoring for someone else, then enter their email address for that entry.
